- This is a Next.js 14+ project using App Router
- Styling is CSS Modules only. No Tailwind. Ever.
- All design tokens are CSS custom properties in globals.css
- No inline styles anywhere in any component
- Sanity CMS is the data source for all content
- Use urlFor() for all Sanity image handling
- All components are functional components with hooks
- Deploy target is Vercel
- Package manager is pnpm
- No em dashes in any generated copy
- Middleware lives in proxy.ts not middleware.ts